-- Rosneft in Talks With Eni on Black Sea Block, Kommersant Says
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2012-04-24T03:54:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/rosneft-in-talks-with-eni-on-black-sea-block-kommersant-says.html
OAO Rosneft,  Russia ’s largest oil
producer, is in talks with  Italy ’s  Eni SpA (ENI)  on a venture to
develop the Val Shatskogo project in Russia’s Black Sea,
 Kommersant  said, citing a person familiar with the negotiations.  Under the proposals, Eni would take a 33.4 percent stake in
the venture to develop the block, while fully funding
exploration and paying Rosneft a bonus if it finds reserves,
Kommersant said, citing the same person.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow at 
